{"tid":1978557,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"預左比人插 我係迷信撚","createTime":"2020-04-18T19:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T06:56:50.000Z","uid":216096,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00973486183f77bcec37edd21284e669c605f667","tid":1978557,"uid":216096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:37:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係一個迷信又咩神都信既人<br />\n果陣新年有人話車公講天網恢恢疏而不漏<br />\n我第二日就去左車公多謝佢為香港人講野<br />\n係2019果陣大家唱聖歌 捱天光<br />\n好多人都好想快d到第二日就出去<br />\n我冇宗教信仰但因為佢地感動左我<br />\n所以亂入左去個團到跟住唱<br />\n我又試過祈禱 因為有人講耶穌會企係公義果邊<br />\n過左好耐 到呢家 我又訓唔著<br />\n呢刻 好懷疑世上有冇神<br />\n訓唔著 純粹鳩up 別認真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab85cce75484725c2c7f5ac8605c6ad3d54152b","tid":1978557,"uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"有無神對你嘅人生嚟講有咩影響"},{"pid":"329b218d657f9e4d238bbd9ecbae097381869556","tid":1978557,"uid":55789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:41:10.000Z","msg":"就算有神 都唔會因為你求佢就會幫你"},{"pid":"3c748a78528a01a8fded3d043aba0e2f958c7c23","tid":1978557,"uid":216096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dab85cce75484725c2c7f5ac8605c6ad3d54152b","tid":1978557,"uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"有無神對你嘅人生嚟講有咩影響"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:45:40.000Z","msg":"如果有神 好似就係最後既希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcec8607b8387a71d8bd0e10e553541eee4c886","tid":1978557,"uid":216096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329b218d657f9e4d238bbd9ecbae097381869556","tid":1978557,"uid":55789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:41:10.000Z","msg":"就算有神 都唔會因為你求佢就會幫你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:48:14.000Z","msg":"但係 假如有神 見到咁多受害者 理應都會感受到人既痛楚同無助 就好似superman咁 會想救人 就算唔直接 都可以間接<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但。。。"},{"pid":"39d22620a2c95602333170